{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaTrackSupportedConstraints.facingMode","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/facingMode","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Media_Streams_API\">Media Streams API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/aspectRatio\"><code>aspectRatio</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/autoGainControl\"><code>autoGainControl</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/channelCount\"><code>channelCount</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/deviceId\"><code>deviceId</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/displaySurface\"><code>displaySurface</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/echoCancellation\"><code>echoCancellation</code></a></li><li><em><code>facingMode</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/frameRate\"><code>frameRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/groupId\"><code>groupId</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/latency\"><code>latency</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/noiseSuppression\"><code>noiseSuppression</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/sampleRate\"><code>sampleRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/sampleSize\"><code>sampleSize</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/volume\"><code>volume</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Media Capture and Streams に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BlobEvent\"><code>BlobEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices\"><code>MediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>MediaDevices.getUserMedia()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrackEvent\"><code>MediaStreamTrackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSettings\"><code>MediaTrackSettings</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/mediaDevices\"><code>Navigator.mediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>VideoStreamTrack</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code></a> 辞書の <strong><code>facingMode</code></strong> プロパティは読み取り専用のブール値で、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/User_agent\">ユーザーエージェント</a>が <code>facingMode</code> の制約に対応している場合にのみ、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaDevices.getSupportedConstraints()</code></a> が返すオブジェクトに存在します (そして <code>true</code> に設定されます)。制約がサポートされていない場合はリストに含まれないので、この値は決して <code>false</code> にはなりません。</p>\n\n<p>対応している制約の辞書にアクセスするには <code>navigator.mediaDevices.getSupportedConstraints()</code>を呼び出してください。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>facingModeConstraintSupported</em> = <em>supportedConstraintsDictionary.</em>facingMode;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>このプロパティは、ユーザーエージェントが <code>facingMode</code> 制約に対応している場合、辞書に存在します (そして、その値は常に <code>true</code> です)。このプロパティが存在しない場合、このプロパティは対応している制約ディクショナリから欠落しており、その値を見ようとすると <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a> になります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> result <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"result\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mediaDevices<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSupportedConstraints</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>facingMode<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Supported!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Not supported!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"結果","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"600\" height=\"80\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/facingMode/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediatracksupportedconstraints-facingmode\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Media Capture and Streams<br><small lang=\"ja\">facingMode の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">勧告候補</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaTrackSupportedConstraints.facingMode","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/facingMode/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Media_Streams_API\">Media Capture and Streams API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaDevices.getSupportedConstraints()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"MediaTrackSupportedConstraints 辞書の facingMode プロパティは読み取り専用のブール値で、ユーザーエージェントが facingMode の制約に対応している場合にのみ、 MediaDevices.getSupportedConstraints() が返すオブジェクトに存在します (そして true に設定されます)。制約がサポートされていない場合はリストに含まれないので、この値は決して false にはなりません。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaTrackSupportedConstraints.facingMode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/mediatracksupportedconstraints/facingmode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/mediatracksupportedconstraints/facingmode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints","title":"MediaTrackSupportedConstraints"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints/facingMode","title":"MediaTrackSupportedConstraints.facingMode"}],"pageTitle":"MediaTrackSupportedConstraints.facingMode - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}